{% block subject %}
    {% spaceless %}
        Application Confirmation: {{ confirmation }}
    {% endspaceless %}
{% endblock subject %}

{% block body_text %}
Hi {{ submission.parentFirstName }} {{submission.parentLastName}},

You recently submitted an application for enrollment in one of the Specialty School Programs at for school year {{ enrollment }}.

Your application has been successfully accepted for consideration!  You will receive additional updates at this email address as the admission process continues.

{% if writing_sample_printout_url is defined and writing_sample_printout_url != '' %}
Your student must complete a Writing Sample in order for your student's application to be processed.  The form must be completed by Friday, February 9, 2018.

Please use the following link to print instructions for your student.

Writing Sample Instructions: {{writing_sample_printout_url}}
{% endif %}

{% if learner_screening_device_printout_url is defined and learner_screening_device_printout_url != '' %}
Your student's homeroom teacher must complete a Learner Screening Device in order for your student's application to be processed.  The form must be completed by Friday, February 16, 2018.

Please use the following link to print instructions for your student's homeroom teacher.

Learner Screening Device Instructions: {{learner_screening_device_printout_url}}
{% endif %}

{% if recommendations_printout_url is defined and recommendations_printout_url != '' %}
Your student's teachers and counselor must complete a Recommendation Form in order for your student's application to be processed.  The form must be completed by Friday, February 16, 2018.

Please use the following link to print instructions for your student's teachers and counselor.

Recommendation Instructions: {{recommendations_printout_url}}
{% endif %}

{% if afterSubmissionDocuments is defined and afterSubmissionDocuments is not empty %}
    {% for document in afterSubmissionDocuments %}
{{document.label}} {{ url('magnet_index')|replace({'app_dev.php/':'','app.php/':''}) }}{{ document.url }}
    {% endfor %}
{% endif %}

For future reference, your confirmation # is {{ confirmation }}. Please retain a copy of this email for your records.

Please add specialty@tusc.k12.al.us to your address list to ensure you receive future status updates of your application.

This is an automated email message from a mailbox that does not accept replies.  {{ 'magnet.contact'|trans|raw }}

Thanks,
Specialty School Program
{% endblock body_text %}

